wiki.summary: “I SEEEEEEE YOU BABY BOI” was first previewed by Playboi Carti on September 15, 2024, via a snippet posted on his alternate Instagram page, opium_00pium, with the caption “YOUNG VAMP LOVE.” He would then play a longer snippet of the song on November 22, 2024, shortly before deleting it from his story. “Baby Boi” is a moniker Carti took in late 2023 during the first stages of the MUSIC rollout—a nickname he initially used for the late R5 Homixide. wiki.content: “I SEEEEEEE YOU BABY BOI” was first previewed by Playboi Carti on September 15, 2024, via a snippet posted on his alternate Instagram page, opium_00pium, with the caption “YOUNG VAMP LOVE.” He would then play a longer snippet of the song on November 22, 2024, shortly before deleting it from his story. “Baby Boi” is a moniker Carti took in late 2023 during the first stages of the MUSIC rollout—a nickname he initially used for the late R5 Homixide. Since taking it on, he got the phrase tattooed on him, and members of his entourage, such as opiumbaby, have referred to him under the name as well. Furthermore, in an Instagram post made the day of MUSIC’s release, he put “BABY BOI OTW” in the caption, possibly hinting at the phrase being a name for his next album. Read more on Last.fm.
